            <scopecontent id="aspace_7994a851041c8abd4ab61b19b6d7bfc6">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The series contains papers obtained by Holloway and used as reference sources while preparing his biography of Crotch. Aside from her autograph manuscript diaries, and her autobiography, also present is a folder of material on Francis Frederick Gordon, editor of the <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                     <part>Advocate of India</part>
                  </title>, a newspaper published in Bombay, India, from 1887 to 1925.</p>
            </scopecontent>
